ock, returns to his roots to write an old-fashioned love story.\n|<ref>{{cite web|title=Watch: Parineeti Chopra sings and announces the title of her new film |url=http://www.ibnlive.com/news/movies/watch-parineeti-chopra-sings-and-announces-the-title-of-her-new-film-1200976.html |publisher=CNN-IBN |date=9 February 2016 |accessdate=9 February 2016 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160212022257/http://www.ibnlive.com/news/movies/watch-parineeti-chopra-sings-and-announces-the-title-of-her-new-film-1200976.html |archivedate=12 February 2016 }}</ref>\n\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |''[[Qaidi Band]]''\n|2017\n|{{sortname|Habib|Faisal|nolink=yes}}\n| [[Aadar Jain]], Anya Singh\n| Seven innocent under-trials give a band performance in the prison to secure their acquittal.\n|<ref>{{cite news|last=Jalan|first=Shivangi|title=Qaidi Band first trailer: An interesting story of undertrials-turned-singers|url=http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/qaidi-band-first-trailer-an-interesting-story-of-undertrials-turned-singers-4756197/|work=The Indian Express|date=18 July 2017|accessdate=23 July 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170721164352/http://indianexpress.com/article/entertainment/bollywood/qaidi-band-first-trailer-an-interesting-story-of-undertrials-turned-singers-4756197/|archive-date=21 July 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |''[[Tiger Zinda Hai]]''\n|2017\n|{{sortname|Ali Abbas|Zafar|nolink=yes}}\n| [[Salman Khan]], [[Katrina Kaif]]\n| Tiger and his wife, Zoya, unite to rescue Indian and Pakistani nurses held hostage by an Islamic terror group.\n|<ref>{{cite news|title=Tiger Zinda Hai: Salman and Katrina\u2019s chemistry is smoking hot in this new pic |url=http://www.deccanchronicle.com/entertainment/bollywood/220317/tiger-zinda-hai-salman-and-katrinas-chemistry-is-smoking-hot-in-this-new-pic.html |work=Deccan Chronicle |date=22 March 2017 |accessdate=4 April 2017 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archiv